          <p class="text-crow-sand-dim text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">Hundreds of blog posts, pull requests, and discussions. Every corner of the Ruby world, every week.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%# Step 2 %>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-8" data-reveal>
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-full border border-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="font-display text-2xl text-gold/40">2</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-2">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-crow-cream mb-2">We curate ruthlessly</h3>
          <p class="text-crow-sand-dim text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">Only the best makes the cut. Each piece is hand-picked and summarized with context that matters to working developers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%# Step 3 %>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-8" data-reveal>
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-full border border-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="font-display text-2xl text-gold/40">3</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-2">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-crow-cream mb-2">You read, we repeat</h3>
          <p class="text-crow-sand-dim text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">A concise, beautifully formatted newsletter lands in your inbox. No spam, no fluff, no tracking pixels. Ever.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

